  "title": "Clinic Assistant (Specialist Clinic, Alt 5.5 days)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage front-desk enquiries, including incoming calls and walk-in patients, ensuring a professional and welcoming experience.</li><li>Assist doctors and nurses in preparing patients for consultations and coordinating required tests.</li><li>Accurately update patient records, process billing, and schedule follow-up appointments.</li><li>Maintain clinic operations, including preparing for the day, monitoring inventory, and ensuring a clean environment.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Nitec or equivalent</li><li>At least 2 years of <strong>front desk and admin experience</strong> in the <strong>healthcare sector.</strong></li><li>Organised, meticulous, and able to manage multiple tasks efficiently.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br />Registration: R1326740</p>",
